FBIS3-33927 "drnes022dd_94008" FBIS-NES-94-022 Document Type:Daily Report 2 Feb 1994 Palestinian Affairs PLO Appoints New Envoy to Washington TA0102142194 Jerusalem AL-QUDS in Arabic 29 Jan 94 p 1 TA0102142194 Jerusalem AL-QUDS Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [By Da'ud Kuttab] [Tex] Jerusalem -- AL-QUDS has learned from Palestinian sources in Tunis that Faruq Qaddumi, head of the PLO Political Department, has signed a letter of appointment designating Hasan 'Abd-al-Rahman as the PLO's envoy in Washington. According to the appointment, 'Abd-al-Rahman will attend to diplomatic affairs with the U.S. State Department and foreign embassies, while Anis al-Barghuthi will continue working with the Palestinian community and organizations in the United States.
